Welcome back to Young, Dumb & 21 and a little special episode! I know it looks short, don't worry the long ones come on Sunday! I wanted to try a little segment where I share my spoken word with you guys. I hope you enjoy it, there is a video on my youtube channel to go with this all. 

I would love some feedback on this, and if you would like me to do this every Wednesday.
